{"tid":1380212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 8月11號深水埗大遊行！","createTime":"2019-07-29T03:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:51:15.000Z","uid":94075,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac981b4a0e1ac878048fb7f38f3bed66697622f","tid":1380212,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"繼8月5號7區集會後，811深水埗接力！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L9QKVkb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9QKVkb.png&h=69c6fba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8 11深水埗區接力開花<br />\n．5大訴求缺一不可<br />\n．掃走黑幫，還我香港<br />\n．踢走黑警，公義城市<br />\n．香港人覺醒🇭🇰<br />\n<br />\n811深水埗遊行<br />\n集合時間：1430<br />\n出發時間：1500<br />\n集合地點：花墟公園<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：花墟公園➡️界限街➡️長沙灣道➡️深水埗運動場<br />\n<br />\n．811深水埗遊行公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NYjxo1U05FXW1fL1zdWkaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNYjxo1U05FXW1fL1zdWkaA&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67dOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=dd160a22\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NYjxo1U05FXW1fL1zdWkaA</a><br />\n<br />\n．811深水埗遊行頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ssp811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fssp811&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67dOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=696ae334\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ssp811</a><br />\n<br />\n．811深水埗義工頻道<br />\n．8 11深水埗區接力開花<br />\n．5大訴求缺一不可<br />\n．掃走黑幫，還我香港<br />\n．踢走黑警，公義城市<br />\n．香港人覺醒🇭🇰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n．全民集結，還我香港🇭🇰<br />\n<br />\n請各位香港人廣傳，支持！<br />\n<br />\n．全民集結，還我香港🇭🇰<br />\n<br />\n請各位香港人廣傳，支持！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oKorsr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oKorsr.png&h=1c227eec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/29/111324_f6752a8231507d0915b6df2902b0117a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F29%2F111324_f6752a8231507d0915b6df2902b0117a.png&h